text: I have been seeing Dr Lee since I was a toddler. Both Dr Low and Dr Lee are kind and wonderful people, and they have been running this clinic since their 20s. Would recommend their clinic to anyone who requires medical services around their neighborhood.

Dr Lee was very kind and accommodating and proceeded with the test anyway.
